{
  ">> Stage I - Garden of Echoes <<": {
    "translation": "第一章  回响花园"
  },
  "Echoing...": {
    "translation": "余音回荡..."
  },
  "Tracing back to the very beginning...": {
    "translation": "追溯一切最初的源头..."
  },
  "Chasing the first dream which has fallen...": {
    "translation": "追寻那已然陨落的初梦..."
  },
  "It all starts where the sky meets the sea.": {
    "translation": "万物始于海天相接之处."
  },
  "It all ends where the sea meets the sky.": {
    "translation": "万物终于海天之交界."
  },
  ">> The place where flowers spread with colors <<": {
    "translation": "繁花盛放之地"
  },
  ">> Stage II - Ruheplatz <<": {
    "translation": "第二章  安息之地"
  },
  ">> The place where our dreams last forever <<": {
    "translation": "美梦永存之地"
  },
  ">> Prayer & Sweet Dreams <<": {
    "translation": "祷告与安眠"
  },
  "What should have died": {
    "translation": "本应消亡之物"
  },
  "still wanders at night": {
    "translation": "仍于暗夜中游荡"
  },
  "Among the pillars of the broken church": {
    "translation": "在残破教堂的立柱之间"
  },
  "shakes frost from its hair": {
    "translation": "抖落发间寒霜"
  },
  "What is already buried": {
    "translation": "早已入土之物"
  },
  "still drinks the moonlight": {
    "translation": "仍啜饮清辉月色"
  },
  "Silver seeps through the coffin cracks": {
    "translation": "银白月光渗过棺木缝隙"
  },
  "wraps round the bone's pale palm": {
    "translation": "缠绕枯骨苍白掌纹"
  },
  "I offer wilted flowers": {
    "translation": "我献上枯萎的花束"
  },
  "offer the lives that've passed": {
    "translation": "祭奠逝去的生灵"
  },
  "Let wind carry the rotten scent": {
    "translation": "任清风携腐朽气息"
  },
  "to bury them in nightmare that lasts": {
    "translation": "将其永埋无尽梦魇"
  },
  "I pray to the empty altar": {
    "translation": "我向着空祭坛祈祷"
  },
  "let the sleeping close their eyes at last": {
    "translation": "愿长眠者终得阖眼"
  },
  "may every waking soul": {
    "translation": "愿每一个清醒灵魂"
  },
  "hold the soft moonlight that sinks upon the pillow cast": {
    "translation": "拥住落于枕畔的柔月"
  },
  "I hear wind through the arch, singing a nameless tune": {
    "translation": "风穿拱门,吟唱无名曲调"
  },
  "I watch the candle flicker, licking the dust on the prayer card's edge": {
    "translation": "烛火摇曳,舔舐祷告卡边缘尘埃"
  },
  "Dark green ivy crawls all over the cross": {
    "translation": "深绿常春藤爬满十字架"
  },
  "The icon's eyes are veiled in thin ash, unseeing": {
    "translation": "圣像双目覆薄灰,不见万物"
  },
  ">> Stage III - Manor of Forget <<": {
    "translation": "第三章  遗忘庄园"
  },
  ">> The place where everything was vanished <<": {
    "translation": "万物消逝之地"
  },
  ">> Elegy of Embers - Volume IV <<": {
    "translation": "残烬挽歌  第四卷"
  },
  "Crown of the Holy Realm": {
    "translation": "圣域之冠"
  },
  "Sceptre of the Holy Blood": {
    "translation": "圣血权杖"
  },
  "Covenant struck with heaven, enthroning God as King": {
    "translation": "与天立约,奉神明为王"
  },
  "Name the realm holy, call the people righteous": {
    "translation": "称疆域为圣,唤子民为公义"
  },
  "The golden dome once held the prayers of thousands of pilgrims": {
    "translation": "鎏金穹顶曾承载万千朝圣者祈愿"
  },
  "The stone seat before the gate engraved a covenant unbroken for a hundred years": {
    "translation": "门前石座刻着百年未碎的誓约"
  },
  "Yet the nightmare came": {
    "translation": "可梦魇终究降临"
  },
  "Yet the fire descended": {
    "translation": "烈火倾泻而下"
  },
  "Stained glass shattered to rubble, the palace gate burned to cinders": {
    "translation": "彩绘玻璃碎作瓦砾,宫门燃为灰烬"
  },
  "Scriptures turned to ash, the hymn lost its voice": {
    "translation": "经书化为飞灰,圣歌不复回响"
  },
  "The people prostrate on the ground, tears falling to ash": {
    "translation": "众生伏于尘土,泪水落作尘埃"
  },
  "No one collects their bones, no one weeps for their passing": {
    "translation": "无人收殓遗骨,无人为逝者哀泣"
  },
  "The old monument lies half-buried in the still-hot dust": {
    "translation": "古老石碑半埋尚有余温的焦土"
  },
  "Crows perch on broken columns, pecking at charred bones": {
    "translation": "乌鸦栖于断柱,啄食焦黑残骨"
  },
  "The breeze carries the embers away": {
    "translation": "微风卷走残存余烬"
  },
  "The fog buries the last echo deep": {
    "translation": "浓雾深埋最后一声回响"
  },
  "Wild grass will sprout from the foot of the broken wall next spring": {
    "translation": "来年春日,断墙脚下将生出野草"
  },
  "When blood is all burned out, where will the soul go?": {
    "translation": "当鲜血燃尽,灵魂将去往何方?"
  },
  ">> Stage IV - Town of Edelweiss <<": {
    "translation": "第四章  雪绒花小镇"
  },
  ">> The place where formerly known as heaven <<": {
    "translation": "曾被称作天国之地"
  },
  ">> Hymn • Blessing Through Suffering <<": {
    "translation": "圣歌  苦难赐福"
  },
  "Truth lies buried deep in mist": {
    "translation": "真相深埋迷雾之下"
  },
  "Hymn echoes inside the skull": {
    "translation": "圣歌在脑海中回荡"
  },
  "The penitent kneels on the stone step": {
    "translation": "忏悔者跪于石阶之上"
  },
  "grinding his palm until it bleeds": {
    "translation": "摩擦掌心直至鲜血淋漓"
  },
  "The scripture is worn white at the edge": {
    "translation": "经书边角磨损泛白"
  },
  "still circles the unfulfilled blessing": {
    "translation": "仍缠绕着未曾兑现的祝福"
  },
  "We receive the blessing that has long rotten": {
    "translation": "我们接纳早已腐朽的祝福"
  },
  "we bear the pain that never ends": {
    "translation": "我们承受无尽不休的苦痛"
  },
  "Whip scars bloom like red flowers on the back": {
    "translation": "鞭痕如红花绽于脊背"
  },
  "Chains choke the throat yet we still cry out the song": {
    "translation": "锁链扼住咽喉,我们仍高唱圣曲"
  },
  "Oh, the blood": {
    "translation": "啊,这鲜血"
  },
  "Oh, the holy blood": {
    "translation": "啊,这神圣之血"
  },
  "The thorn crown frays the warm skin of the brow": {
    "translation": "荆棘冠划破额头温热肌肤"
  },
  "The nail print burns an inscription in the palm": {
    "translation": "钉痕在掌心烙下印记"
  },
  "Salvation dissolved in the blood": {
    "translation": "救赎融于鲜血之中"
  },
  "Blasphemy dissolved in the holy blood": {
    "translation": "亵渎消散于圣血之内"
  },
  "God says suffering itself is the path of trial": {
    "translation": "神明言道,苦难本就是试炼之路"
  },
  "Only souls refined by fire deserve the kingdom above": {
    "translation": "唯有烈火淬炼的灵魂方能抵达天国"
  },
  "Praise the holy believers": {
    "translation": "赞颂圣洁的信徒"
  },
  "Praise the immortal Sovereign": {
    "translation": "赞颂不朽的主宰"
  },
  "......": {
    "translation": "......"
  },
  ">> Stage V - Throne of Divine <<": {
    "translation": "第五章  神之王座"
  },
  ">> Whispers in Ash <<": {
    "translation": "灰烬低语"
  },
  "I see the dream like ash": {
    "translation": "我见残梦如飞灰"
  },
  "burning in the dark of night": {
    "translation": "于暗夜之中燃烧"
  },
  "The stars weep, the moon chokes": {
    "translation": "星辰垂泪,月色哽咽"
  },
  "weaving a shroud of rest for those who never come back": {
    "translation": "为一去不返之人编织安息裹布"
  },
  "Cold mist creeps over the grass-choked path": {
    "translation": "冷雾漫过荒草遮蔽的小径"
  },
  "Dew dampens the unmarked stone slab": {
    "translation": "露水打湿无碑石板"
  },
  "Who walks the path we trod before": {
    "translation": "谁踏过我们曾走过的路"
  },
  "Who has forgotten the first light we were born with": {
    "translation": "谁遗忘了与生俱来的初光"
  },
  "Wind tugs crumpled paper past my ankle": {
    "translation": "清风卷皱纸拂过脚踝"
  },
  "an unfinished prayer, drifting into the distance": {
    "translation": "一段未完成的祷告,飘向远方"
  },
  "All blood is burned out": {
    "translation": "所有鲜血已然燃尽"
  },
  "only embers are left whispering": {
    "translation": "只剩余烬低声呢喃"
  },
  "Moonlight seeps through the crack in the old wall": {
    "translation": "月光透过旧墙缝隙渗入"
  },
  "spreading a layer of silver over the long-closed coffin": {
    "translation": "为尘封已久的棺木覆上一层银辉"
  },
  "He says:": {
    "translation": "他言道"
  },
  "\"I knew you once, I saw you once": {
    "translation": "我曾识你,我曾见你"
  },
  "I carved you into the heart of silence": {
    "translation": "我将你刻入寂静深处"
  },
  "Now you return to dust": {
    "translation": "如今你重归尘土"
  },
  "just as you came from dust\"": {
    "translation": "一如你自尘土中来"
  },
  ">> Map made by Lastims <<": {
    "translation": "地图制作：Lastims"
  },
  ">> Huge thanks to Inailuz!!! <<": {
    "translation": "万分感谢Inailuz!"
  },
  "雾林镇每日的颂歌照常传颂": {
    "translation": "雾林镇每日的颂歌照常传颂"
  },
  "悄然而至的污秽无人在意": {
    "translation": "悄然而至的污秽无人在意"
  },
  "腐败蔓延，侵蚀心智，将镇上的居民化作他物": {
    "translation": "腐败蔓延,侵蚀心智,将镇上的居民化作他物"
  },
  "异乡的旅人啊，原初之血注视着您": {
    "translation": "异乡的旅人啊,原初之血注视着您"
  },
  "恳请您结束这场肆虐已久的腐朽盛宴": {
    "translation": "恳请您结束这场肆虐已久的腐朽盛宴"
  },
  "Barrier will break in 30s": {
    "translation": "屏障将在30秒后失效"
